### FastAPI Integration

#### [MODIFY] [main.py](file:///c:/Users/ACER/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/Intelligent_AI_Interview_Platform/ai-services/main.py)

- Import `GazeTracker` and add per-session `gaze_trackers` dict (same pattern as `face_verifiers`)
- In `/api/analyze-frame`: create/reuse `GazeTracker` per session, call [analyze_frame(frame)](file:///c:/Users/ACER/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/Intelligent_AI_Interview_Platform/ai-services/main.py#242-314), merge gaze results into the response
- In `/api/session/{session_id}`: add gaze summary stats to the report

