## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
```bash
cd c:\Users\ACER\OneDrive\Documents\GitHub\Intelligent_AI_Interview_Platform\ai-services
python test_all_services.py
```

### Manual Verification
1. Verify `python -c "from gaze_tracker import GazeTracker; t = GazeTracker(); print('OK')"` works
2. Verify the module can process a dummy frame without crashing:
   ```bash
   python -c "from gaze_tracker import GazeTracker; import numpy as np; t = GazeTracker(); print(t.analyze_frame(np.zeros((480,640,3), dtype=np.uint8)))"
   ```
